description: Previously (undefeated) ranked #2 Isis was not just defeated by the Pirate, she was destroyed. The Pirate plundered the Number 2 wrestler, and in round four she took Isis in the ass. Watch as the Pirate utterly defeats the Goddess. Watch as Isis is made to suffer though her very first ass fucking on camera. The Pirate is for real folks and her total victory over Isis is proof of that.
title: The Pirate (4-1) vs. The Goddess (5-0)
